                                    <h3 style="color: white; font-size: 1.75rem; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                                        <iconify-icon icon="solar:user-circle-bold-duotone" style="color: #8a2be2; margin-right: 0.5rem; font-size: 2rem; vertical-align: middle;"></iconify-icon>
                                        Cr√©er un nouveau compte
                                    </h3>
